PrecisAppointment of the Hon. JOHN W. McCLUNG, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Alberta, as ADMINISTRATOR of the GOVERNMENT OF ALBERTA, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor during the absence, illness or other incapacity of the latter.
